definitions.name: data
definitions.contract:
wishlists: _view.wishlistOverview.meta.wishlistCollection.wishlists,

    addAllProductsToCart: _view.addAllAvailableProductsToCartForm,

        parameters: {
            wishlistName: _view.wishlistName
        }
    }
